"pid":"2e10942312d1407608034cc0d7c9e1512b2c3b12","tid":42812,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z03203c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ03203c.jpg&h=956187af&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個樣真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有波你睇仲咁多野講, 你唔上我上呀"},{"pid":"e1be06b715258de9ee377acfe29f160efb632bb1","tid":42812,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">粉閪</span>"},{"pid":"5af41dc14077688c026aed2d15ec992c9b7d7fa0","tid":42812,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z03203c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ03203c.jpg&h=956187af&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個樣真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有波你睇仲咁多野講, 你唔上我上呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無潮文想睇返，有奶又話無腳有腳又話無樣，齊哂又話雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b95fb2a892f9cb3565f577fb2342320ca6b157","tid":42812,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個樣真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有波你睇仲咁多野講, 你唔上我上呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無潮文想睇返，有奶又話無腳有腳又話無樣，齊哂又話雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇啲高登仔<br />\n無圖就跪晒要睇圖<br />\n變左黃蛙又瓜瓜嘈<br />\n睇咗就扮晒野話條女普通，好差<br />\n係度嫌三嫌四<br />\n人地夠索又話人對波無E<br />\n人地波大又話個樣唔掂，隻眼細<br />\n人地樣樣都有又話人mk...咩化晒妝唔好睇<br />\n人地打扮多少少又話人mk...著到成隻雞咁<br />\n好喇好喇,到搵到個完美嘅又話人ps<br />\n屌你老母! 除咗識話人做雞之外仲識啲咩!<br />\n你班仆街根本連女都無得屌呀!<br />\n上高登就扮撚晒大少，乜春都唔屌<br />\n死翻去現實就見到舊肥豬肉都扯旗<br />\n唔好講話比欣宜你地屌唔屌<br />\n我諗比個白韻琴你地啲毒男都成班餓狗搶屎咁搶住屌呀白小姐呀!"},{"pid":"0f7e2a5d3658915bce04c3969683d5bf3e9e60ab","tid":42812,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a3617e7f860a11c8d4892706b2ebe504a978b5","tid":42812,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7a9e407ce2440fd84c28b483f5cd2434421ae6","tid":42812,"uid":11511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有波你睇仲咁多野講, 你唔上我上呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無潮文想睇返，有奶又話無腳有腳又話無樣，齊哂又話雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇啲高登仔<br />\n無圖就跪晒要睇圖<br />\n變左黃蛙又瓜瓜嘈<br />\n睇咗就扮晒野話條女普通，好差<br />\n係度嫌三嫌四<br />\n人地夠索又話人對波無E<br />\n人地波大又話個樣唔掂，隻眼細<br />\n人地樣樣都有又話人mk...咩化晒妝唔好睇<br />\n人地打扮多少少又話人mk...著到成隻雞咁<br />\n好喇好喇,到搵到個完美嘅又話人ps<br />\n屌你老母! 除咗識話人做雞之外仲識啲咩!<br />\n你班仆街根本連女都無得屌呀!<br />\n上高登就扮撚晒大少，乜春都唔屌<br />\n死翻去現實就見到舊肥豬肉都扯旗<br />\n唔好講話比欣宜你地屌唔屌<br />\n我諗比個白韻琴你地啲毒男都成班餓狗搶屎咁搶住屌呀白小姐呀!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7113ee179ed11eb3fca785fa4f05f86e828e075","tid":42812,"uid":9479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7c2ce6a1827a1c17b9226cab9f3ad7d01de06e","tid":42812,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無潮文想睇